snippet.title: One Night at Flumpty's UI for Console demonstration
snippet.description:
Please make sure to SUBSCRIBE so you won't miss us trying to scare you!

All three Flumpty games are currently being worked on for consoles! Here is a taste of the UI elements in action for ONAF1. Will have more soon!

ONAF 1 & 2 currently available on Mobile!

ONAF 1 Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.clickteam.onaf1&hl=en_US&gl=US
ONAF 1 iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/one-night-at-flumptys/id1536627815
ONAF 2 Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.clickteam.onaf2&hl=en_US&gl=US
ONAF 2 iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/one-night-at-flumptys-2/id1536628438

#FNAF #ONAF #HORROR #JUMPSCARE
